OL,3,C#21m rehab centre designed to reduce
OL,4,Cpressure on hospitals
OL,6,FPhysiotherapy patients say they have
OL,7,Fnew-found hope for recovery after a
OL,8,F#21m rehabilitation centre has opened.
OL,10,FThe clinical team at Western Community
OL,11,FHospital in Southampton gave their
OL,12,Fviews on what features they wanted to
OL,13,Fsee at the new on-site rehab centre.
OL,15,FIt has been designed to help patients
OL,16,Frecovery quickly and free up space on
OL,17,Facute hospital wards.
