OL,3,C#21m rehab centre designed to reduce
OL,4,Cpressure on hospitals
OL,6,FThe site, funded by Hampshire and Isle
OL,7,Fof Wight NHS Foundation Trust, is
OL,8,Fthought to be the first of its kind in
OL,9,Fthe area.
OL,11,FThe rooms have been built with
OL,12,Ffeatures to reduce patient injuries
OL,13,Fand improve mental wellbeing. The
OL,14,Frehab centre also has a gym, kitchen,
OL,15,Frestaurant, day area and courtyard.
