OL,6,FMark Maffey, Architect and Estates
OL,7,FProject Manager at Hampshire and Isle
OL,8,Fof Wight NHS Foundation Trust said:
OL,9,F"From the outset we've been working
OL,10,Fwith the clinical teams who have
OL,11,Fprovided us the brief for almost
OL,12,Feverything we've done in the building.
OL,14,F"The single bedrooms are a good
OL,15,Fexample of that, as we know that by
OL,16,Fplacing the bed on the same side of
OL,17,Fthe room as the en-suite, there will
OL,18,Fbe fewer slips and trips and falls.
