OL,3,C#21m rehab centre designed to reduce
OL,4,Cpressure on hospitals
OL,6,F"We also know that by giving patients
OL,7,Fa view of the outside world and of
OL,8,Fnature, it will help them recover
OL,9,Fquicker."
OL,11,FThe kitchen area on-site is used to
OL,12,Fhelp patients get back into daily
OL,13,Froutines and take on day-to-day tasks,
OL,14,Fsuch as making a cup of tea of making
OL,15,Fbreakfast.
OL,17,FConsultant Geriatrician Lauren Webb
OL,18,Fsaid: "It allows patients to really
OL,19,Ftest what they can do for themselves.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
