OL,3,C#21m rehab centre designed to reduce
OL,4,Cpressure on hospitals
OL,6,F"As part of the right to rehab as we
OL,7,Fall have, we want our patients to get
OL,8,Fas good as possible and back to as
OL,9,Fmuch independence as they can.
OL,11,F"Quite a few patients come in here and
OL,12,Fdo their tea assessments, some of them
OL,13,Fmake their breakfast. They've been
OL,14,Fable to make it in a real kitchen
OL,15,Fenvironment, just like home."
