OL,3,C#21m rehab centre designed to reduce
OL,4,Cpressure on hospitals
OL,6,FBy making sure people are well-
OL,7,Fequipped to go back into their daily
OL,8,Froutines, it is hoped fewer patients
OL,9,Fwill re-injure themselves after being
OL,10,Fdischarged and need to go back to
OL,11,Fhospital.
OL,13,FDavid Haydn Thomas, who is one of the
OL,14,Ffirst patients at the rehab centre,
OL,15,Fsaid: "The first day I came here I saw
OL,16,Fthey had a restaurant, 'The Grove', I
OL,17,Fwent and had a cup of tea and I sat
OL,18,Foutside.
OL,20,F"I've been in hospital for so long, I
OL,21,Frealised I hadn't been outside."
