OL,3,C#21m rehab centre designed to reduce
OL,4,Cpressure on hospitals
OL,6,F20-year-old university student Amy
OL,7,FLeneve is in recovery for a spinal
OL,8,Finjury after an accident while
OL,9,Ftrampolining abroad.
OL,11,FAmy Leneve said: "I've been doing
OL,12,Fphysio everyday since I got here. My
OL,13,Fgoal is to be out by Christmas, I'm
OL,14,Fsure that would be everyone's goal.
OL,15,FBut in the long-run I want to go back
OL,16,Fto university, I want to complete that.
OL,18,F"I want to get up and walking again
OL,19,Fand get a semi-normal life back and
OL,20,Fnot let this get the best of me."
